This business case presentation, developed from a product management perspective, reimagines the traditional gas station as a sustainable and user-centric public space for the evolving EV era. It details a strategic vision for a future-ready fueling experience, incorporating market analysis, user needs, and proposed solutions like solar-powered infrastructure, seamless app integration, and diversified retail offerings. The project emphasizes addressing challenges in the automotive energy sector through innovative product development and a focus on customer satisfaction and environmental impact.






